Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:35.63,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(410,390)\fsp5\blur2}贵重之物 花鸟风月的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,右邊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種茶碗居然是寶物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 嚴格說來是護送
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比一般的運輸任務危險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍貴的花鳥風月 是國寶級珍品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的價值足以買下一兩座山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們負責將它護送到展覽會場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大的保險箱 裡面是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防不測 綱手大人派我前來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外你聽說其他事沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了寶物之外就沒什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的兩個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到「閒雜人等不得入內」的告示嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們奉綱手大人之命前來執行運輸任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 這是證明文件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 要倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開這裡 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼呆 快擋下它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是來執行任務的吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不趕快工作 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死也不能讓它倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 這個保險箱怎麼處理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才差點完蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者為任務而死不是理所當然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫大哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是任務委託人 近衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 既然沒死 趕快出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用牙狼牙 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要用螺旋丸教訓他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別那麼認真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你們有沒有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一開始就興奮過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會兒沒力氣了我們可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡跟你們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮過頭 所以弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正時間充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能下去拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 好像時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞下去可就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什麼 你想幹嗎 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高空彈跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也沒事 我會替你收屍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 鳴人 小心後面 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者為任務而亡很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死一次給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 不要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用螺旋丸教訓他 難消我心頭之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 冷靜點 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情自然一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 怎麼看都是我最自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣一點也不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位仁兄 留步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子裡似乎裝著重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們替你們護送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把東西給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會完成任務的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 其實也不是什麼重要的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 根本不值一提啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們胡說什麼啊 這當然很重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面可是國寶級珍品 你們忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是花鳥風月啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比人命還尊貴的花鳥風月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可別小看它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在亂說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你還搞不清狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦 管他什麼狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不許任何人侮辱花鳥風月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比性命還重要的寶物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算死了也毫無怨言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我還有課 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責擋住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 你帶著近衛門大哥快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又來了一票人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼跟我一起逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想辦法啊 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一起上吧 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在打群架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 又在打群架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真悲哀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 的確很悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 笨蛋們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天一定要好好教訓你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙 赤丸 牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於掌握到花鳥風月的下落了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 待在這裡不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲了 快滾出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話什麼 笨蛋 快想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說 我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好教訓他們吧 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然視線被封鎖 那就靠嗅覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們見識一下吧 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底躲哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物花鳥風月 我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擬獸忍法.獸人分身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來用這招 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中動態標記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼鹹鹹的 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你在哪裡 趕快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你怎麼這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓狗四處撒尿 此仇不報非君子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教訓我們之前 還是先把寶物追回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此 就該把寶物給我保管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑借赤丸的空中動態標記 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能找到搶走寶物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 赤丸 對方還沒走遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了 終於到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來奪寶貝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狂妄 打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥快去追那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙 我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蟊賊 休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都結束了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西還我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子 本想放你一條生路的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把花鳥風月還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我一條生路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花鳥風月可是比生命更珍貴的超級寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打一開始就不在乎自己的性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這兩個下忍真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都灰頭土臉的 還敢說我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你們一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把花鳥風月帶到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走 這裡就要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把花鳥風月帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花鳥風月…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你不要動 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢把手伸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你到底想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管它了 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忍者就該拚命保護花鳥風月才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 別理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他想死 就隨他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花鳥風月…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們差點完蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者為任務而死不是理所當然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 既然沒死 趕快出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是花鳥風月啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比人命還尊貴的花鳥風月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可別小看它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我一條生路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花鳥風月可是比生命更珍貴的超級寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打一開始就不在乎自己的性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上沒有比生命更重要的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹嗎愁眉苦臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說你們沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了寶物 任務也就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一個 你說的倒是輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大哥的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不凡的名器花鳥風月 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作者是國寶級大師 近衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個花鳥風月是大哥親手打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是委託人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託人難道就不可以是國寶級製作人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 怎麼看都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡跟你們不同 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的性命的確比寶物重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們雖然是下忍 不過挺能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕緊打造一個超越花鳥風月的名作了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的任務是把被捕的不忍押送回京
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是一群逃亡忍者組成的強盜團伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲稱自己不是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用忍者的力量做壞事 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你們應該明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他不忍成員可能會中途搭救他了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要確保押送任務成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.30,0:23:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是不忍
